<section class="py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-primary tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">How It Works</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-light tracking-tight text-heading mb-4">
        A bottleneck? <span class="font-medium">We've got you covered.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-body text-base leading-relaxed">
        Pick any task across Operations, Marketing, or Sales. Your AI employee steps in,
        works 24/7, and handles it — so you break through bottlenecks without hiring.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary-light text-primary">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-xs font-bold w-6 h-6 mb-3">1</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-2">Pick any task, any department</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Stuck on a report? Need campaigns launched? Sales follow-ups piling up? Tell us where it hurts — Operations, Marketing, or Sales — and we'll get your AI employee on it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary-light text-primary">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-xs font-bold w-6 h-6 mb-3">2</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-2">We deploy. We manage.</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          We set up your AI Employee on a secure VPS, connect it to your tools, and keep it running. 
          You never have to worry about uptime, updates, or maintenance — <strong class="text-heading font-medium">your new employee never sleeps</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary-light text-primary">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-xs font-bold w-6 h-6 mb-3">3</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-2">They work and improve.</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Your AI Employee learns from every interaction. Over time, they get faster, smarter, 
          and more tailored to your business — <strong class="text-heading font-medium">self-evolving into a better employee</strong> without you lifting a finger.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
